headline: Jacobs’ New Security And Rail Wins Versus Valuation And Momentum Signals
summary: Jacobs Solutions, NYSE:J, and PA Consulting secured a four year extension to lead the UK's National Security Science and Research program. Jacobs won new US defense infrastructure work tied to missile defense facilities. The company was also awarded contracts on San Diego rail and Texas coastal resilience projects.
